@everyone Please could all the 40:60 voters rechoose between 50:50 and 60:40 so that we have a 50% majority vote on either of them.

I personally think the 60:40 is the way to go because it allows those people actively marketing off the marketplace to offer a better rate, like 50:50 without their hardwork being undercut.

But either way if we get a majority vote, it will silence the people saying that this is not what the majority want

